<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Digital Resume</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="digitalresume.css">
</head>


<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Louis Savon</h1>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
        <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section id="home">
      <h1>HEY, I'AM LOUIS SAVON</h1>
      <h2>Future computer engineer</h2>
      <h3>Passionate about the possibilities offered by computing.</h3>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <h2>About me</h2>
      <p>Student at Epitech Marseille — passionate about technology, travel and innovation. Curious, sociable and motivated, I turn every discovery into a concrete project.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="experience">
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <p>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by readable content when looking at its layout. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="skills">
      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. It has survived five centuries and the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged.</p>
    </section>

    <form action="/ma-page-de-traitement" method="post">
  <ul>
    <li>
      <label for="name">Nom&nbsp;:</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="user_name" />
    </li>
    <li>
      <label for="mail">E-mail&nbsp;:</label>
      <input type="email" id="mail" name="user_email" />
    </li>
    <li>
      <label for="msg">Message&nbsp;:</label>
      <textarea id="msg" name="user_message"></textarea>
    </li>
    
    <div class="button">
        <button type="submit">Envoyer le message</button>
    </div>
  </ul>
    </form>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-left">
      <p>© 2025 Louis Savon — No AI was harmed during the creation of this CV.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-right">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/louis-savon-a46714354/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/LouiSvon" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/louis.svon/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
